movida - a free movie collection manager.
 Version: 0.9

 movida helps you to manage your movie collection so you can quickly know if you have a movie and what that movie is all about.

 If you need help building the movida source code, please read the INSTALL file or visit the official website: http://movida.sourceforge.net

And now enjoy movida or shut down the computer and have a life!

The movida team